snippet.title: Proun's Abstract Landscapes trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW ON PC! Get it at www.proun-game.com

The beautiful abstract world of Proun, in slow motion. Proun is a strange racing game in a world of geometric objects and large coloured surfaces. You avoid obstacles by rotating around a cable in order to gain as much speed as possible. There is no up or down; there is only the cable to which you are attached.

The music in this video is by Igorski. Check out more of his awesome songs on www.igorski.nl.
